version_description: One more with few different chords. This one can be played along the original song with capo on 1st fret.
Chords are from the live performance Anssi Kela ja isot biisit.
A Pave Maijanen cover song by Anssi Kela from the TV-show Vain Elamaa (2015).
Unreleased song, based on this video https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmCZpuYhJ-A please check out for strumming.
This version has included section names and is easy to play off of which is what a song written in chord format should be.
The intro has the same chord progression as the verses. On the recording it sounds like only the first few strings are strummed (all down).
